      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/01/01_athAtaH_panchayajnAH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अथातः पञ्चयज्ञाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथातः पञ्चयज्ञाः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/01/01_athAtaH_panchayajnAH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Now (follow) the five sacrifices:&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/01/01_athAtaH_panchayajnAH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथातः पञ्चयज्ञाः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/01/02_devayajno_bhUtayajnaH_pitRy.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;02 देवयज्ञो भूतयज्ञः पितृयज्ञो ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;देवयज्ञो भूतयज्ञः पितृयज्ञो ब्रह्मयज्ञो मनुष्ययज्ञ इति २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/01/02_devayajno_bhUtayajnaH_pitRy.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The sacrifice to the Gods, the sacrifice to the Beings, the sacrifice to the Fathers, the sacrifice to Brahman, the sacrifice to men.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/01/02_devayajno_bhUtayajnaH_pitRy.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;देवयज्ञो भूतयज्ञः पितृयज्ञो ब्रह्मयज्ञो मनुष्ययज्ञ इति २&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०२</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/02/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/02/01_atha_svAdhyAyavidhiH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अथ स्वाध्यायविधिः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथ स्वाध्यायविधिः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/02/01_atha_svAdhyAyavidhiH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . Now the rules how one should recite (the Vedic texts) for one&amp;rsquo;s self.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/02/01_atha_svAdhyAyavidhiH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथ स्वाध्यायविधिः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/02/02_prAgvodagvA_grAmAnniShkramy.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;02 प्राग्वोदग्वा ग्रामान्निष्क्रम्याप आप्लुत्य ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;प्राग्वोदग्वा ग्रामान्निष्क्रम्याप आप्लुत्य शुचौ देशे यज्ञोपवीत्याचम्याक्लिन्नवासा दर्भाणां महदुपस्तीर्य प्राक्कूलानान्तेषु प्राङ्मुख उपविश्योपस्थं कृत्वा दक्षिणोत्तरौ पाणी सन्धाय पवित्रवन्तौ विज्ञायतेऽपां वा एष ओषधीनां रसो यद्दर्भाः सरसमेव तद्ब्रह्म करोति द्यावापृथिव्योः सन्धिमीक्षमाणः सम्मील्य वा यथा वा युक्तमात्मानं मन्येत तथा युक्तोऽधीयीत स्वाध्यायम् २&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०३</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/03/01_atha_svAdhyAyamadhIyIta_Rch.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अथ स्वाध्यायमधीयीत ऋचो ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथ स्वाध्यायमधीयीत ऋचो यजूंषि सामान्यथर्वाङ्गिरसो ब्राह्मणानि कल्पान्गाथा नाराशंसीरितिहासपराणानीति १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/03/01_atha_svAdhyAyamadhIyIta_Rch.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . He then should recite for himself (the following texts, viz.) the Ṛcas, the Yajus, the Sāmans, the Atharvan and Aṅgiras hymns, the Brāhmaṇas, the Kalpa (Sūtras), the Gāthās, the (texts in honour of kings and heroes, called) Nārāśaṃsīs, the Itihāsas and Purāṇas.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/03/01_atha_svAdhyAyamadhIyIta_Rch.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथ स्वाध्यायमधीयीत ऋचो यजूंषि सामान्यथर्वाङ्गिरसो ब्राह्मणानि कल्पान्गाथा नाराशंसीरितिहासपराणानीति १&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०४</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/04/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/04/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/04/01_devatAstarpayati_prajApatir.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 देवतास्तर्पयति प्रजापतिर्ब्रह्मा वेदा ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;देवतास्तर्पयति प्रजापतिर्ब्रह्मा वेदा देवा ऋषयः सर्वाणि च्छन्दांस्योङ्कारो वषट्कारो व्याहृतयः सावित्री यज्ञा द्यावापृथिवी अन्तरिक्षमहोरात्राणि साङ्ख्याः सिद्धाः समुद्रा नद्यो गिरयः क्षेत्रौषधिवनस्पतिगन्धर्वाप्सरसो नागा वयांसि गावः साध्या विप्रा यक्षा रक्षांसि भूतान्येवमन्तानि १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/04/01_devatAstarpayati_prajApatir.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . He satiates the deities: &amp;lsquo;Prajāpati, Brahman, the Vedas, the gods, the Ṛṣis, all metres, the word Om, the word Vaṣaṭ, the Vyāhṛtis, the Sāvitrī, the sacrifices, Heaven and Earth, the air, days and nights, the numbers, the Siddhas, the oceans, the rivers, the mountains, the fields, herbs, trees, Gandharvas and Apsaras, the snakes, the birds, the cows, the Sādhyas, the Vipras, the Yakṣas, the Rakṣas, the beings that have these (Rakṣas, &amp;amp;c.) at their end.&amp;rsquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०५</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/05/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/05/</guid>
