    <item>
      <title>०७</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/07/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/07/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/07/01_avyAdhitanchatsvapantamAdit.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अव्याधितञ्चत्स्वपन्तमादित्योऽभ्यस्तमियाद्वाग्यतोऽनुपविशन्रात्रिशेषम्भूत्वा येन सूर्यज्योतिषा ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अव्याधितञ्चत्स्वपन्तमादित्योऽभ्यस्तमियाद्वाग्यतोऽनुपविशन्रात्रिशेषम्भूत्वा येन सूर्यज्योतिषा बाधसे तम इति पञ्चभिरादित्यमुपतिष्ठेत १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/07/01_avyAdhitanchatsvapantamAdit.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;If the sun sets while he is sleeping without being sick, he should spend the rest of the night keeping silence, without sitting down, and should worship the sun (when it rises) with the five (verses), &amp;lsquo;The light, O sun, by which thou destroyest darkness&amp;rsquo; (Rig-veda X, 37, 4 seq.).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/07/01_avyAdhitanchatsvapantamAdit.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अव्याधितञ्चत्स्वपन्तमादित्योऽभ्यस्तमियाद्वाग्यतोऽनुपविशन्रात्रिशेषम्भूत्वा येन सूर्यज्योतिषा बाधसे तम इति पञ्चभिरादित्यमुपतिष्ठेत १&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०८</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/08/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/08/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/08/01_athaitAnyupakalpayIta_samAv.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अथैतान्युपकल्पयीत समावर्त्यमाने मणिङ् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथैतान्युपकल्पयीत समावर्त्यमाने मणिं कुण्डले वस्त्रयुगं छत्रमुपानद्युगं दण्डं स्रजमुन्मर्दनमनुलेपनमाञ्जनमुष्णीषमित्यात्मने चाचार्याय च १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/08/01_athaitAnyupakalpayIta_samAv.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Now when returning (home from his teacher) he should get the following things, viz. a jewel (to be tied round the neck), two ear-rings, a pair of garments, a parasol, a pair of shoes, a staff, a wreath, (pounded seed of the Karañja fruit) for rubbing with, ointment, eye salve, a turban; (all that) for himself and for the teacher.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/3/08/01_athaitAnyupakalpayIta_samAv.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथैतान्युपकल्पयीत समावर्त्यमाने मणिं कुण्डले वस्त्रयुगं छत्रमुपानद्युगं दण्डं स्रजमुन्मर्दनमनुलेपनमाञ्जनमुष्णीषमित्यात्मने चाचार्याय च १&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०९</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/09/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/09/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/3/09/01_smRtannindA_cha_vidyA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 स्मृतन्निन्दा च विद्या ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;स्मृतन्निन्दा च विद्या च श्रद्धा प्रज्ञा च पञ्चमी ।&#xA;इष्टन्दत्तमधीतञ्च कृतं सत्यं श्रुतं व्रतम् । यदग्ने सेन्द्रस्य सप्रजापतिकस्य सऋषिकस्य सऋषिराजन्यस्य सपितृकस्य सपितृराजन्यस्य समनुष्यस्य समनुष्यराजन्यस्य साकाशस्य सातीकाशस्य सानुकाशस्य सप्रतीकाशस्य सदेवमनुष्यस्य सगन्धर्वाप्सरस्कस्य सहारण्यैश्च पशुभिर्ग्राम्यैश्च यन्म आत्मन आत्मनि व्रतन्तन्मे सर्वव्रतमिदमहमग्ने सर्वव्रतो भवामि स्वाहेति १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/3/09/01_smRtannindA_cha_vidyA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . (He says), &amp;lsquo;Memory and reproach and knowledge, faith, and wisdom as the fifth, what is sacrificed, and what is given, and what is studied, and what is done, truth, learning, vow -&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>१०</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/3/10/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
